    "where the mean and variance in q(y t-1 |y t, y 0) are obtained from Eqs. 17 and 18.",
    "The posterior distribution plays a dual role in parameterizing the reverse diffusion chain and formulating a variational lower bound on the log-likelihood of the chain.",
    "Moving forward, we will explore using generative adversarial networks to parameterize this denoising model.",
